verbose_text: In agreement, we found a slight paired-pulse depression under control conditions (PPR (I 1 / I 2) : 0.84 +/- 0.015), and hyaluronidase treatment significantly increased the PPR (PPR (I 1 / I 2) : 0.90 +/- 0.008; p < 0.001; XREF_FIG H and 7I).
evidence: hyaluronidase treatment significantly increased the PPR
